{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1779175954538,"sessionID":"ses_1c0d9a155ffeCYKJHSTB41oREt","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"glob","callID":"call_02_amRiDdtBIM4wuvPJA92n9143","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"pattern":".claude-project/nestfind/design/**"},"output":"/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/variations/C-02-dashboard.html\n/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/variations/A-03-detail.html\n/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/variations/B-02-dashboard.html\n/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/variations/C-01-landing.html\n/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/variations/B-01-landing.html\n/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/variations/A-02-dashboard.html\n/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/variations/A-01-landing.html\n/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/DESIGN_SYSTEM_C.md\n/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/DESIGN_SYSTEM_B.md\n/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/DESIGN_SYSTEM_A.md\n/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/DOMAIN_RESEARCH.md","metadata":{"count":11,"truncated":false},"title":"","time":{"start":1779175954215,"end":1779175954536}},"id":"prt_e3f269380001VZVkOCY35VxvZj","sessionID":"ses_1c0d9a155ffeCYKJHSTB41oREt","messageID":"msg_e3f2661f6001IUkslraS4ff0Lh"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1779175957067,"sessionID":"ses_1c0d9a155ffeCYKJHSTB41oREt","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_03_p7mBDVLcuyHW1gWMbQwK4199","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/docs/PROJECT_API.md","limit":80},"output":"<path>/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/docs/PROJECT_API.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # PROJECT_API\n2: \n3: NestFind API Contract — canonical reference for all API endpoints.\n4: \n5: **Base URL:** `http://localhost:3000/api`\n6: \n7: ---\n8: \n9: ## Endpoints\n10: \n11: ---\n12: \n13: ### Authentication\n14: \n15: ---\n16: \n17: #### Register\n18: \n19: | Method | Path | Auth |\n20: |--------|------|------|\n21: | `POST` | `/auth/register` | Public |\n22: \n23: **Description:** Self-service registration. Creates a new user account with the `renter` role. Returns user data and sets httpOnly cookies for access + refresh tokens.\n24: \n25: **Request Body:**\n26: ```json\n27: {\n28:   \"name\": \"string (2–100 chars, required)\",\n29:   \"email\": \"string (valid email, required)\",\n30:   \"password\": \"string (min 8 chars, required)\",\n31:   \"phone\": \"string (optional, max 20 chars)\"\n32: }\n33: ```\n34: \n35: **Success Response** `201 Created`:\n36: ```json\n37: {\n38:   \"success\": true,\n39:   \"statusCode\": 201,\n40:   \"message\": \"User registered successfully\",\n41:   \"data\": {\n42:     \"id\": \"uuid\",\n43:     \"name\": \"string\",\n44:     \"email\": \"string\",\n45:     \"phone\": \"string | null\",\n46:     \"role\": \"renter\",\n47:     \"status\": \"active\",\n48:     \"createdAt\": \"ISO 8601 timestamp\",\n49:     \"updatedAt\": \"ISO 8601 timestamp\"\n50:   },\n51:   \"timestamp\": \"ISO 8601 timestamp\",\n52:   \"path\": \"/api/auth/register\"\n53: }\n54: ```\n55: \n56: **Error Responses:**\n57: - `400` — Validation failed (missing fields, invalid email, weak password)\n58: - `409` — Email already registered\n59: \n60: ---\n61: \n62: #### Login\n63: \n64: | Method | Path | Auth |\n65: |--------|------|------|\n66: | `POST` | `/auth/login` | Public |\n67: \n68: **Description:** Authenticate with email and password. Sets httpOnly cookies: `access_token` (1h) and `refresh_token` (7d).\n69: \n70: **Request Body:**\n71: ```json\n72: {\n73:   \"email\": \"string (required)\",\n74:   \"password\": \"string (required)\"\n75: }\n76: ```\n77: \n78: **Success Response** `200 OK`:\n79: ```json\n80: {\n\n(Showing lines 1-80 of 1621. Use offset=81 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# PROJECT_API\n\nNestFind API Contract — canonical reference for all API endpoints.\n\n**Base URL:** `http://localhost:3000/api`\n\n---\n\n## Endpoints\n\n---\n\n### Authentication\n\n---\n\n#### Register\n\n| Method | Path | Auth |\n|--------|------|------|","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":".claude-project/nestfind/docs/PROJECT_API.md","time":{"start":1779175956751,"end":1779175957065}},"id":"prt_e3f2698bd001RyVHrte7Gi2yle","sessionID":"ses_1c0d9a155ffeCYKJHSTB41oREt","messageID":"msg_e3f2661f6001IUkslraS4ff0Lh"}}
